Italy Aims to Become Russia’s Third-Largest Trading Partner

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i   a n d   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-06-02T12:50:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/italy-aims-to-become-russia-s-third-largest-trading-partner.html
Italy wants to become  Russia ’s third-
biggest commercial partner, Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi 
said at a press conference in  Rome  today.  “We are Russia’s fourth-largest trade partner,”
Berlusconi said. “We have ambitions, and we would like in a
short time to become the third largest.”  Italy has always been on the same wavelength as Russia on
international issues, Berlusconi said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
